sion of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參見","title":"參見","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function\"><code>Function</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"描述","id":"描述"},{"text":"屬性","id":"屬性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"規範","id":"規範"},{"text":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性"},{"text":"參見","id":"參見"}],"summary":"Function.prototype 屬性表示 Function 的原型物件。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"locale":"en-US","title":"Function","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/function","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/function/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"pageTitle":"Function.prototype | MDN","noIndexing":true}}